            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Irena Rosenwasser</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#rosenwasserI" start="4316.403" end="x">So there was no purpose for me to return, because I, too, wish to emigrate to America, and have received an affidavit already in Belsen . . . </span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="4327.475" end="x">Aha . . . </span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Irena Rosenwasser</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#rosenwasserI" start="4328.028" end="x"> . . . to go to America, and on that basis I have come to <a class="placename" href="#vothL13">Paris</a>.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="4332.514" end="x">Oh, You are in France for the first time?</span>
