                <span class="">Irena Rosenwasser</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#rosenwasserI" start="4336.819" end="x">I was never in France before. In a week I found employment, a position here with the <a class="term" href="#vothG_ajdc">Joint</a>, and since then I work here.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
